{"tid":1457668,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[全世界入] 今日之後討論去留方法要改革","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:10:55.000Z","uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d4dce71be717e52ac88b26355f4df71138cc01f9","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"利申: 行過上前線 但唔係每次都企最前<br />\n聽過好多前線討論有板有眼 一樣係舉正反理據由現場決定<br />\n<br />\n我絕對支持現場決定, 因為現場會有氣氛,環境判斷同突發野<br />\n亦不得不否認冷氣軍師有上帝視角, 缺點係容易謠言滿天飛<br />\n<br />\n所以!!!<br />\n<br />\n係討論重大戰術行動 (e.g. 去留/衝) 既時候<br />\n我懇求<span style=\"color: red;\">所有冷氣軍師唔好就咁叫人走</span><br />\n因為你地唔應該係決定現場人士去留既人<br />\n你地可以做既係<span style=\"color: red;\">列出PROS AND CONS</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正反理據</span>一一列明 將所有現場難掌握既資訊列低<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">重要: 所有未FC唔肯定既資訊必須列明未證實</span><br />\n而希望現場亦會<span style=\"color: red;\">根據現場環境/狀況</span> 考慮冷氣軍師所提出既Pros and cons<span style=\"color: red;\">最後作出決定</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子: 今日機場去留 (純例子如有錯輕屌)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">留</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">PROS: </span><br />\n- 護送剩餘旅客<br />\n- 繼續文宣比抵港旅客<br />\n- 比壓力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">CONS: </span><br />\n- 6點可能清場 (source:? / 未FC)<br />\n- 今日已達目的: 所有航班停飛, 唔會再有未起飛來港航班抵港<br />\n- 有鬼會可能會衝禁區, 令列機特合理清場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">去</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">PROS:</span><br />\n- 今日已達目的 (同上)<br />\n- 長仗長打, 留得青山在<br />\n- 等到狗有行動先走就太遲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">CONS:</span><br />\n- 機場有手足落單就未必救到<br />\n- 士氣會散<br />\n- 去留人士衝突<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">建議方案 (唔一定要跟)</span>: 可以走, 但一旦有航班復飛馬上折返機場增援<br />\n<br />\n重申一次 我絕對支持現場決定 <br />\n我明白大家都好嬲 見到咁多位手足自己人屌自己人好心痛<br />\n所以希望有個更加完善既決策系統比冷氣軍師同現場有更加理性既討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地要屌既唔要係自己人<br />\n要屌爆林鄭同狗!!!!!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"b08af24246e9ffe2af43e944b26160f1299fc099","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"支持前線決定"},{"pid":"254bd26a7d08504b33c88e70a96a9a99e278e7c1","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"推 我地要改革"},{"pid":"e7419c28bfd72e0bff3f62819d6d6e25b10e30ff","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"唔要自己人屌自己人"},{"pid":"97e6cadcefd8734ae8ae4f5ccab6225fbdab498a","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"6b7275fa21efcdf7b31b1bd16a187a2057b9054c","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:05:20.000Z","msg":"屌林奠老母"},{"pid":"b875749ba8c19ad7f3e1c5d2a811d76a488135f4","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"9c020cd7be085bb29e1a598737856e9b2b002b75","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"我要一個完善既討論機制"},{"pid":"c9f95a66b9e7af9b2be1814bd9ea719a5e4d0d3f","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"唔要消息亂傳"},{"pid":"7fc0fae089cad611075e72744cb01f7e7a7e796e","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:06:47.000Z","msg":"推呀 冷氣軍師入"},{"pid":"d5f3a534b5ffb408d819560e92293947f0742213","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師唔好幫前線落決定!<br />\n列PROS AND CONS!!!!"},{"pid":"ea34534b83ed5157fbff0b6ed44b4cf753fc30c2","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:07:30.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師唔好幫前線落決定!<br />\n列PROS AND CONS!!!!"},{"pid":"60748d98c1760c27dbe83dd7a413ca350d226469","tid":1457668,"uid":263839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"